Class PSOAncestorFolderSlotContentFinder

All Implemented Interfaces:
com.percussion.extension.IPSExtension, com.percussion.services.assembly.IPSSlotContentFinder
public class PSOAncestorFolderSlotContentFinder
extends com.percussion.services.assembly.impl.finder.PSBaseSlotContentFinder

Finds a single content item of a given content type in the current folder of the assembly item or an ancestor folder. The finder first looks in the current folder and if not found then proceeds up the folder tree until an item with the given content type is found. If no item is found the slot will be empty. The slot will always have either one or zero items.

adamgent
